{"tid":2113701,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"武肺測試慢慢由支那化驗公司主導 香港疫情會更唔明確","createTime":"2020-07-18T09:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T02:06:44.000Z","uid":137078,"like":51,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"785dff3e7bb4e56220bc75b99bb4da74ce14f5b2","tid":2113701,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T09:58:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200718/F33P5FZZX4WRNXVVT2RCS2TLKY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200718%2FF33P5FZZX4WRNXVVT2RCS2TLKY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=40eebce9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200718%2FF33P5FZZX4WRNXVVT2RCS2TLKY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=5e10996e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200718/F33P5FZZX4WRNXVVT2RCS2TLKY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今早《蘋果》記者曾欲前往太平工業園三樓興建中的實驗室單位瞭解情況，但遭保安喝止。據《蘋果》所獲資料，興建中的實驗室，與華大基因旗下的華昇診斷中心有關，而「華昇」將獲政府聘用為至少11萬港人的樣本進行武漢肺炎測試。<br />\n<br />\n#武漢肺炎<br />\n【大埔工廈做內地病毒檢測實驗室 街坊蒙在鼓裏感驚慌 保安阻記者採訪】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3hdGFaI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3hdGFaI&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=5827e86b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3hdGFaI</a><br />\n【否認內地實驗室將港人資料「送中」 董事胡定旭：採樣職員不會知檢測者身份】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ODrGdY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ODrGdY&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=51e03c0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ODrGdY</a><br />\n【內地病毒檢測實驗室登陸大埔工廈 與商戶共用升降機惹恐慌】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3eCp3ng\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3eCp3ng&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=a1df812d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3eCp3ng</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望有人留意吓<br />\n先唔講港共直接送利益比三間支那背景化驗所做咁大量嘅測試<br />\n到底測試準確度有幾高<br />\nDNA資料會唔會被送中<br />\n公司背景可以睇返，華昇呢間野係專做 基因排序測試<br />\n<br />\n港版健康碼（監控碼？）又有港共政府大力推+再出發大聯盟班垃圾推，咁邊個係幕後推手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n若果佢嘅測試準確度係冇咁高<br />\n當大部分測試結果（十幾萬人都做）慢慢由佢哋呢啲支那公司主導<br />\n香港可能係另一個武肺城市<br />\n即使新聞嘅透明度依家都仲未死晒<br />\n但喺源頭嘅嗰個測試結果都唔准，咁點樣報道都係冇意思<br />\n<br />\n呢個係我自己幻想最差結果"},{"pid":"922df16b0ca95023bc0d58da4dc868b7817c222a","tid":2113701,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:00:57.000Z","msg":"最後咪沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9399075449d57fb96010b85b20074aa2576f09aa","tid":2113701,"uid":13013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a84754ced9afbc050f10977a1daee00c6ee399","tid":2113701,"uid":34047,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:02:53.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n根本借疫情黎推健康碼<br />\n成件事明明就人禍<br />\n勁多轄免檢疫既人<br />\n加埋銅鑼灣返工果班國安<br />\n之前比大紀言訪問<br />\n睇住佢地個口罩都未戴好<br />\n<br />\n你話來源不明？<br />\n係因為怕比人知來源係支國<br />\n支國0確診根本係笑話咋掛<br />\n<br />\n係時候宣傳<br />\n等公眾知第三波繼續係人禍<br />\n食店執笠 勁多人失業<br />\n都係因為港共唔做好邊境把關而造成<br />\n<br />\n果班藍屍成日屌人阻佢返工<br />\n而家港共政府特登搞到你冇得返工<br />\n分分鐘直頭冇埋份工<br />\n你仲係咪繼續撐政府呀？"},{"pid":"153853f4cce768130d94b76f4fce13df9be28c89","tid":2113701,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:03:03.000Z","m